Heat grill. Season chops with salt and pepper. Whisk together remaining ingredients. Place chops on plate and drizzle each with 1 teaspoon of the herb mixture. Rub into chops until coated. Place chops on grill over medium-high heat. Cover and cook 8 to 10 minutes for medium rare or until desired doneness, turning once. Whisk remaining herb mixture again. Drizzle over cooked lamb chops.